query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-bluetooth',
'breakpoints',
'chatbot',
'core-animation',
'directive',
'publish-subscribe',
'pyinstaller',
'python-3.7',
'quotes',
'recaptcha',
'scenebuilder',
'string-comparison',
'userform');
